reviews.text: I like how economical their handmade pasta is. The set could be as sixty something Hong Kong dollars for dinner set. To be honest, the pasta was not really taste like homemade, or maybe I am not professional enough, but the taste was good. I would say kind of too oily but with this price, absolutely acceptable. And the location and environment were good too. Recommend!
Affordable, clean and very good service. The pasta taste and al dente texture is always just right. Would visit this place at least once a week if I lived close by!
The pasta was good, however the seating was awful, seems they don't want customers having a comfortable meal.
Definitely worst spaghetti in the town. Poor presentation and taste. No worth to try.

reviews.text: Great services, hot pot with good music performance.
Very nice with live music singer, and can dedicate a song if u like♡food is ok, service is good.
We went in new year holiday, there are just too many people there and it was short staffed
Food ok, live music with hot pot seem not very acceptable for me.

Hainanese Coconut Chicken hot pot restaurant with live band, but the band is not that professional with handicap in English and many Cantonese songs. The coconut pot itself is good, but other hot pot dishes are only limited choices. One of their famous King Crab legs dumpling have only very limited crab legs meat.

reviews.text: 地方舒適招呼週到，晚飯火煱菜式豐富，下午飲茶略嫌點心款式少，但味道不錯。
食物其本0K，招呼服務都不錯。
食物質素, 服務非常臻錯。價錢亦算合理,4人餐連beer,埋單約$1800

有現場音樂表演，但不夠大眾化，當晚食客都是中年老年佔八成，還有國內人，需改變。
食物質素一般過一般。
價錢普通，但份量減半，同等價錢去第二間食等如佢兩碟，變相貴價！漏單問題嚴重！！味道不能評價，因為漏哂單無得食！！！

reviews.text: 茄子牛豚手工意粉，帶少辣，好味，茄子好靚但咬落去太多油。
主打fushion 和風意大利粉，味道不錯，食材新鮮，唯款式不多，意大利粉外，別無選擇
開業初期，食物，招呼，衛生，效率都做得不錯，員工肯定攞高分。可以維持多久，視乎坐寫字樓管理那班有無用心。九個月後的今日 (190215) 已經只剩一顆星。
